{"tid":797924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「活人復原法+3D列印」　1200年唐朝公主重生了","createTime":"2018-08-29T02:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T12:13:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3c23018e2ede2c35a69e7bc5501ad47966f70c0d","tid":797924,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"陝西西安的西北大學2日使用「國內現代人顱面數據庫」，透過顱骨裡的碳元素和人類學的分析，再提取數據庫裡相同年齡的人的軟組織作為依據，最後成功復原唐朝李倕公主以及秦代侍女的面貌，最後再用3D列印技術，讓古人重現立體的容貌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3460/3460227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3460%2F3460227.jpg&h=12c2452c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲復原出來的秦代婦女。（圖／翻攝自微博／網易財經）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，李倕是唐高祖李淵的第五代孫女。2001年－2003年時，陝西省考古研究院在西安理工大學新校區基建工地上，挖到一處大型墓葬群，一共清出182座墓葬，包括漢、唐、宋、元、明和清代的墓葬，其中一個就是唐公主李倕的墓。據墓志銘記載，李倕在唐玄宗開元24年病逝，得年25歲，換算到現在已有1200多年的時間。<br />\n<br />\n其實在2013年時，就已經有專家展示過李倕復原的容貌。由於公主的整個下頜骨是缺損的，所以研究人員是將她的顱骨做CT掃描，在通過調配數據庫中累積的將近千對顱骨和面容資料比對，最後重新將公主的下頜骨建構出來。<br />\n<br />\n成立考古隊已有62年的陝西西安的西北大學，透過學校建立的國內現代人顱面數據庫，加上科研人員對古人顱骨的「碳14」鑑定和人類學分析，能夠推斷出入葬時的年齡範圍。接著再從現有的數據庫中，提取出與目標相同年齡段的人的軟組織厚度為依據，通過「3D列印技術」復原古人面貌。<br />\n<br />\n至於這個顱面復原的技術，周明全表示，關鍵是尋找顱骨和面容的關係。首先先從「活人」開始，也就是把某人頭部的CT數據掃描進電腦，然後用3D技術模擬出一樣的顱骨。回推復原容貌，再把復原容貌與真人進行比對，發現相似度可以非常高。這些年他們累積了近千份像這樣子的樣本，然後再用這樣的方法來復原古人的容貌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3460/3460226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3460%2F3460226.jpg&h=de6845b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼用數據取樣並3D列印古人的復原樣。（圖／翻攝自微博／網易財經）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3460/3460229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3460%2F3460229.jpg&h=0748571e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180803/1227314.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180803%2F1227314.htm&d=%2F7PvxGVesDDcZSZb%2Fw0AhZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=4684ae9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180803/1227314.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2018/8/20180803_095613_617.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2018%2F8%2F20180803_095613_617.png&h=775ae5b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ece6da138bbb2963ba8ded0a340e9a7372095d7","tid":797924,"uid":196751,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:12:09.000Z","msg":"買個hottoys學下雕塑先啦"},{"pid":"1a1772445dc771c2ead9e31a1fcaa4ca88ec231e","tid":797924,"uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"秦代侍女似印傭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb99eec24fa758867362da78a6df9ee54cca7ca9","tid":797924,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ece6da138bbb2963ba8ded0a340e9a7372095d7","tid":797924,"uid":196751,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:12:09.000Z","msg":"買個hottoys學下雕塑先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3360bc62627e1b946aacf6e74b3c961b1fc49b","tid":797924,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b664af1ed9c3d01a15ed27160bebd56678100aa0","tid":797924,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:15:48.000Z","msg":"南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b7ab5d4fa23288eef6caa9c59de2240a51e366","tid":797924,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"eb99eec24fa758867362da78a6df9ee54cca7ca9","ti